A new entrant into the sport betting industry, Luckybet.ng, has announced Finidi George as its Brand Ambassador. George, famous for the number seven (NO.7) jersey is by far the best player to have played for the Nigerian Super Eagles. At the googletastic launch ceremony, Luckybet.ng revealed its plans to become Nigeria’s most innovative, engaging, fun and entertainment gaming brand. The former Nigerian international and UEFA Champions League winner, declared that his reason for accepting the role is his belief in the guiding principles and philosophy of the Luckybet.ng brand. “Luckybet.ng provides a world class series of entertaining and rewarding opportunities, and its state of the art platform will empower Nigerians during this economic situation by tapping into the passion points of Nigerians. “I think they have shown that they care, they are willing to create jobs for over 20,000 people using a distinctive franchise model and with the presence of soccer, you will see that it is a combination of everything, and I key into that.  I am glad to be a part of this too because I have a role to play in helping punters to bet wisely,” George said. 